and antiterrorism agencies.”

63
00:02:42,110 --> 00:02:44,000
Because anyone who is against the Party,

64
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,920
must be sick.

65
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:47,470
Like the young woman in Hubei province

66
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:48,990
