for complaining about the lack of treatment
she got at a hospital.

68
00:02:52,690 --> 00:02:56,250
“She was coerced into making a ‘confession’
video

69
00:02:56,250 --> 00:03:00,030
in which she told her followers not to ‘spread
false rumors’

70
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:03,140
and to respect the country and its communist
leaders.”

71
00:03:03,140 --> 00:03:07,500
Fortunately, these kinds of complaints will
happen less and less.

72
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,820
Because censors are using WeChat and Twitter

73
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:13,150
