82
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:42,740
Sharing is caring.

83
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:46,520
Of course most grocery stores still manage
to get supplies.

84
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:49,160
Unless police come in to confiscate the goods.

85
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,460
Don’t worry,

86
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:53,150
